title: GMO & Dense - Shell And Seal EP (2014)
description:
Artist: GMO
Artist: Dense
Title: Shell and Seal
Cat. Nr.: CLCD089DG
Release Date: 27-10-2014
Format: Digital
Style: Chill Out / Electronica / Trance
Label: Cosmicleaf Records

GMO and Dense, both known for their excellent solo projects, reunite their forces on a new Cosmicleaf release, offering a more chilled-out dimension of their musical cosmos. With relaxing summer beats, smooth instrumental elements and a nostalgic sunset vibe, this is the perfect soundtrack to drive home after a long day at the beach with friends
